metadata.name: Year of the Rabbit #1
metadata.description:
Year of the Rabbit is the most adorable generated NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain inspired by a real resilient rabbit called Chiko in Sydney, Australia. This collection in total 5,000 randomly generated and stylistically curated NFTs with each NFT generated from 75+ traits. These traits and symbols portray the celebration spirits for Lunar New Year.
2023 is the Year of the Water Rabbit which comes once in a 60-year cycle based on 5 elemental signs. The Year of Water Rabbit represents hope and prosperity. Coming after the battle with a global pandemic, the Year of Water Rabbit will help us to recover and reconnect with new opportunities. Like rabbits, when we tap into our personal power and confidence, we can achieve our goals despite challenges along the way.
A community-driven project, the holders of the token can participate in exclusive events such as NFT games, raffles, community giveaways and educational Webinars.
